snippet.textDisplay:
Kevin spacey is innocent.All the charges against him were dropped which means the accusors were just making stuff up to extort some money out of him and earn some social points and become popular by riding the wave of metoo movement.Big props to Kevin for staying strong throughout the last two years.I can only imagine how hard it must have been to cope and put yourself together when the whole world is against you.Given how much media attention he has received ,the mass hysteria and the extensive investigation done by law enforcement over the last two years,he would already be in jail if there was even a slight evidence of him commiting any crimes.He has been cleared of any charges by the law enforcement as they couldn't find a single evidence of any wrongdoings .
So I will trust the judgement of our legal system over any mass hysteria or internet conspiracy theorists . The people who think he is still guilty after all of this either have to provide hard and concrete evidence or they should shut up . In a democracy,every person should be given right to be presumed innocent until proven guilty.I am going to accord that same right written in our constitution to Kevin and everyone else should too.
